biography: Rasmus, a name synonymous with precision and strategic play on the greens, hails from the esteemed Vihti Golf Club. Known for his contemplative approach to the game, Rasmus brings a calculated intensity to every tournament.

While Rasmus has only graced the Hector Trophée once with his presence, his impact is memorable. Though he has not yet claimed either the coveted Hector Trophée or the Victor Trophy, his participation adds a layer of intrigue to the competition.
Currently considered retired from Hector Trophée events, the possibility remains open for a surprise return. Should he decide to compete again, spectators can anticipate a display of skillful golf.
